0.5.name: wordpress/supra-mongodb-manager
0.5.description: Do you have a mongodb collection you want to administer in the backend? Perhaps you are a developer and interfaced mongo somehwere else in the site. This plugin provides an ajax based crud administration for the documents of each configured collection.
